## Aims

The aim is to develop an advanced AI-based learning tool specifically for Vietnamese high school students. The application will cater to the unique demands and requirements of the high school curriculum, offering a comprehensive learning experience.

## Motivation

The motivation behind this project is to address the increasing challenges students face in their studies while leveraging technological advancements. Current AI-based learning tools lack the ability to provide complete and clear explanations. This project seeks to fill that gap by developing an AI learning tool with superior capabilities.

## Features

- AI assistant with thorough explanations.
- Flexible question input methods: text, scanning, photos, voice.
- Subject categorization and targeted assistance.
- Virtual assistant for guiding subject selection and tool usage.
- Integration of generative AI to provide accurate solutions.

## Landscape

In the landscape of AI-based learning tools, there are existing platforms with limitations. This project aims to compete by providing a more advanced, comprehensive, and user-friendly solution tailored to Vietnamese high school students' needs.

## Plans and Progress

Detailed progress and planning stages, including idea initiation, idea generation, website development, and project timeline, are outlined.

## Roles

Each team member's roles and responsibilities are defined, ensuring an equitable distribution of tasks to accomplish the project goals.

## Scope and Limits

The scope and limitations of the project are outlined, focusing on high school students and specific subjects, leveraging generative AI while ensuring the accuracy and quality of the learning experience.

## Feature Design

Detailed feature design, including authentication, landing page, subject-wise tools, and download options, are explained to give an overview of the application's functionalities.

